{"tid":1450213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【連儂everywhere】住係香港既麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:16:15.000Z","uid":200405,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89c0f5b4c491eb8939bc1cc1762760e3a7940511","tid":1450213,"uid":200405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:25:11.000Z","msg":"相信過左今日一伇大家都心灰意冷 <br />\n首先講句 香港人撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基於近日見到我住個區幅連儂牆都畀人撕得七七八八 所以我有個提議：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>就係print啲文宣當傳單咁塞入每家每戶既門口</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我有見過真係有上咗年紀嘅人會主動行過去連儂牆睇 但都要本人願意行過去先得<br />\n但我塞入你門口 就無得你唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且單機做又得 <br />\n怕事既就唔洗冒住喺街痴文宣個時畀廢老屌既風險<br />\n尤其係住公屋既巴絲 <br />\n出入容易 公屋又多撐警廢老<br />\n文宣主打721 警黑合作 無緣無故畀警察拉 老屈等等<br />\n<br />\n文宣既開頭最好係<br />\n<br />\n「你是香港人嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「你有兒女嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「你想你的下一代在香港落地生根嗎」<br />\n<br />\n依類關於廢老本人/下一代既Topic 吸引佢地睇落去<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"9360b691869a99af4d1f5cfdbad2d6782f32809c","tid":1450213,"uid":200405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:26:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ea9894c309975ab1bdac6e39c156e9f20270bfd","tid":1450213,"uid":200405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:27:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74070a15eb7be65f9a21bb58b2622c854e358df0","tid":1450213,"uid":200405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:36:15.000Z","msg":"有無人想同我一齊做！！！"},{"pid":"1435426666cc756052ca6116905eba7f334b0a2d","tid":1450213,"uid":200405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:39:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2221617a05c9ffad98f4cf71b1b45684d10359b2","tid":1450213,"uid":200405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:39:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf7f93b89855559057a482bf24a70cac76c81222","tid":1450213,"uid":200405,"like":0,"dislike":0,